#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "2009&ndash;2010: amnesia, T(A)ILS, and their ancestors"
msgstr "2009-2010: amnesia, T(A)ILS i els seus avantpassats"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Today, Tails is based on Debian, Tor, and GNOME. We inherit from their work "
"and try to contribute back in order to create a healthy ecosystem of "
"reliable, secure, and usable tools."
msgstr ""
"Avui, Tails es basa en Debian, Tor i GNOME. Heretem del seu treball i "
"intentem contribuir-hi per crear un ecosistema saludable d'eines fiables, "
"segures i utilitzables."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"When we started the *amnesia* project back in 2009, other projects before us "
"paved the way to what is Tails today:"
msgstr ""
"Quan vam començar el projecte *amnesia* l'any 2009, altres projectes abans "
"que nosaltres van obrir el camí cap al que és avui Tails:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"[Knoppix](http://www.knoppix.org/), born in 2000 and still alive today, was "
"the first popular live Linux distribution. Back then, it was a "
"groundbreaking achievement to be able to start and use Linux without going "
"through lengthy, very complex, and uncertain Linux install \"parties\". "
"Knoppix was primarily designed for convenience and diagnosis."
msgstr ""
"[Knoppix](http://www.knoppix.org/), nascuda l'any 2000 i encara viu avui "
"dia, va ser la primera distribució popular de Linux en directe. Aleshores, "
"va ser un assoliment innovador poder iniciar i utilitzar Linux sense passar "
"per «parts» d'instal·lació de Linux llargues, molt complexes i incertes. "
"Knoppix es va dissenyar principalment per a la comoditat i el diagnòstic."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"[ELE](https://web.archive.org/web/20050422130010/http://www.northernsecurity."
"net:80/download/ele/), born in 2005 and based on Damn Small Linux, [Anonym."
"OS](https://web.archive.org/web/20060212030338/http://theory.kaos.to:80/"
"projects.html), born in 2006 and based on OpenBSD, and [Incognito](https://"
"web.archive.org/web/20071213084719/http://www.browseanonymouslyanywhere.com/"
"incognito/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=28&Itemid=41), born in "
"2007 and based on Gentoo, pushed the concept of live operating systems a bit "
"further by focusing on security, online anonymity, and the use of Tor."
msgstr ""
"[ELE](https://web.archive.org/web/20050422130010/http://www.northernsecurity."
"net:80/download/ele/), nascuda l'any 2005 i basada en Damn Small Linux, "
"[Anonym.OS](https://web.archive.org/web/20060212030338/http://theory.kaos."
"to:80/projects.html), nascut el 2006 i basat en OpenBSD, i [Incognito]"
"(https://web.archive.org/web/20071213084719/http://www."
"browseanonymouslyanywhere.com/incognito/index.php?"
"option=com_content&task=view&id=28&Itemid=41), nascuda el 2007 i basada en "
"Gentoo, van impulsar el concepte de sistemes operatius en directe una mica "
"més centrant-se en la seguretat, l'anonimat en línia i l'ús de Tor."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  *Incognito*\n"
"  was the first live operating system to include a full set of\n"
"  applications preconfigured to go through Tor (browser, email\n"
"  client, IRC client, etc.), offer a persistent *Home*\n"
"  directory, and even allow hosting onion services.\n"
"  *Incognito* was also the first live operating system to receive an\n"
"  [official recognition from the Tor\n"
"  Project](https://blog.torproject.org/incognito-and-tor-project-sign-licensing-agreement).\n"
msgstr ""
"  *Incognito*\n"
"  va ser el primer sistema operatiu en directe que va incloure un conjunt complet\n"
"  d'aplicacions preconfigurades per passar per Tor (navegador, client de correu electrònic,\n"
"  client IRC, etc.), ofereix un directori *Home*\n"
"  persistent, i fins i tot permet allotjar serveis d'onion.\n"
"  *Incognito* també va ser el primer sistema operatiu en directe que va rebre un\n"
"  [reconeixement oficial del Projecte\n"
"  Tor](https://blog.torproject.org/incognito-and-tor-project-sign-licensing-agreement).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  The original author of *Incognito*, *Pat Double*, resigned in 2007 and *anonym*, who\n"
"  still works for Tails today, took over the maintenance.\n"
msgstr ""
"  L'autor original d'*Incognito*, *Pat Double*, va dimitir el 2007 i *anonym*, que\n"
"  encara treballa avui per a Tails, es va fer càrrec del manteniment.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"On August 16 2009, *intrigeri* announced the first release of *amnesia* on "
"the [*tor-talk* mailing list](https://lists.torproject.org/pipermail/tor-"
"talk/2009-August/002667.html)."
msgstr ""
"El 16 d'agost de 2009, *intrigeri* va anunciar el primer llançament "
"d'*amnesia* a la llista de correu [*tor-talk*](https://lists.torproject.org/"
"pipermail/tor-talk/2009-August/002667.html)."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"In March 2010, *Incognito* was declared dead and *amnesia* its \"[spiritual "
"successor](https://web.archive.org/web/20100728224716/http://www."
"anonymityanywhere.com:80/incognito)\".  Some weeks later, *amnesia* would be "
"renamed *T(A)ILS*, *The Amnesic Incognito Live System*, to act the fusion "
"between *amnesia* and *Incognito*."
msgstr ""
"El març de 2010, *Incognito* va ser declarat mort i *amnesia* el seu "
"«[successor espiritual](https://web.archive.org/web/20100728224716/http://"
"www.anonymityanywhere.com:80/incognito)». Unes setmanes més tard, *amnesia* "
"passaria a anomenar-se *T(A)ILS*, *The Amnesic Incognito Live System*, per "
"fer la fusió entre *amnesia* i *Incognito*."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  We quickly realized that having parenthesis in our name looked very\n"
"  radical but was quite confusing and finally settled on *Tails* in 2011.\n"
"  Eight years later, we still see most people on the Internet write it\n"
"  TAILS though it's never been written in all caps on our website.\n"
msgstr ""
"  Ràpidament ens vam adonar que tenir parèntesis al nostre nom semblava molt\n"
"  radical, però era bastant confús i finalment ens vam decidir per *Tails* el 2011.\n"
"  Vuit anys després, encara veiem que la majoria de gent a Internet escriu\n"
"  TAILS encara que mai s'ha escrit en majúscules al nostre lloc web.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "  Hey people, it's Tails not TAILS!\n"
msgstr "  Hola gent, és Tails no TAILS!\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This is how *amnesia* 0.2 and our website looked like in 2009. The browser "
"was *Iceweasel* with *Tor Button* and the Tor controller was *TorK*."
msgstr ""
"Així es veia *amnesia* 0.2 i el nostre lloc web l'any 2009. El navegador era "
"*Iceweasel* amb *Tor Button* i el controlador Tor era *TorK*."

