"Lee](https://theintercept.com/2014/10/28/smuggling-snowden-secrets/)  have "
"repeatedly stated the importance of Tails for their work and supported us in "
"many ways."
msgstr ""
"L'abril de 2014, Freedom of the Press Foundation va llançar la primera "
"campanya de crowdfunding per a Tails i va revelar que Tails «ha estat "
