#, no-wrap
msgid "2015-2019 - Maturity, user experience, and automation"
msgstr "2015-2019 - Maduresa, experiència d'usuari i automatització"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"In May 2014, the UX team at [NUMA Paris](https://web.archive.org/"
"web/20140524130455/http://events.numaparis.com/Evenements/Apero-Experience-"
"Utilisateur-Tails-The-Amnesic-Incognito-Live-System)  invited us to organize "
"a usability testing session of Tails with journalists. We asked participants "
"to do slightly complex tasks such as establishing an encrypted conversation "
"with someone else using *Pidgin*.  Reality hit us hard when all the "
"journalists in the room encountered problems to either install, start, or "
"connect Tails to Tor. We realized that, despite having laid down most of the "
"core features in Tails 1.0, we still had a lot of work to do to make Tails "
"easy to use by most people."
msgstr ""
"El maig de 2014, l'equip d'UX de [NUMA Paris](https://web.archive.org/"
"web/20140524130455/http://events.numaparis.com/Evenements/Apero-Experience-"
"Utilisateur-Tails-The-Amnesic -Incognito-Live-System) ens va convidar a "
"organitzar una sessió de proves d'usabilitat de Tails amb periodistes. Vam "
"demanar als participants que fessin tasques lleugerament complexes, com ara "
"establir una conversa encriptada amb algú altre mitjançant *Pidgin*. La "
"realitat ens va afectar molt quan tots els periodistes de la sala van trobar "
"problemes per instal·lar, iniciar o connectar Tails a Tor. Ens vam adonar "
"que, tot i haver establert la majoria de les funcions bàsiques de Tails 1.0, "
"encara teníem molta feina per fer perquè Tails fos fàcil d'utilitzar per la "
"majoria de la gent."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Since then, we focused our work on 3 aspects of the project that don't bring "
"in so many new features but rather ensure its long term sustainability and "
"growth: user experience, continuous integration, and project sustainability."
msgstr ""
"Des d'aleshores, hem centrat el nostre treball en 3 aspectes del projecte "
"que no aporten tantes novetats sinó que garanteixen la seva sostenibilitat i "
"creixement a llarg termini: experiència d'usuari, integració contínua i "
"sostenibilitat del projecte."

#. type: Title ###
#, no-wrap
msgid "User experience"
msgstr "Experiència d'usuari"

#. type: Plain text
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Since these first usability tests in 2014, we systematically relied on "
#| "user-centered design practices to ensure that all the major changes that "
#| "we do in Tails are making it easier to use. We conducted 10 sessions of "
#| "usability tests, used [paper prototypes](https://simplysecure.org/blog/"
#| "formative-testing), conducted [[!tails_blueprint veracrypt "
#| "desc=\"quantitative surveys\"]], and defined better our audience using "
#| "[[personas|contribute/personas]]."
msgid ""
"Since these first usability tests in 2014, we systematically relied on user-"
"centered design practices to ensure that all the major changes that we do in "
"Tails are making it easier to use. We conducted 10 sessions of usability "
"tests, used paper prototypes, conducted [[!tails_blueprint veracrypt "
"desc=\"quantitative surveys\"]], and defined better our audience using "
"[[personas|contribute/personas]]."
msgstr ""
"Des d'aquestes primeres proves d'usabilitat el 2014, ens hem basat "
"sistemàticament en pràctiques de disseny centrades en l'usuari per assegurar-"
"nos que tots els canvis importants que fem a Tails el fan més fàcil "
"d'utilitzar. Vam realitzar 10 sessions de proves d'usabilitat, vam utilitzar "
"[prototips en paper](https://simplysecure.org/blog/formative-testing), vam "
"realitzar [[!tails_blueprint veracrypt desc=\"enquestes quantitatives\"]] i "
"vam definir millor el nostre públic utilitzant [[persones|contribute/"
"personas]]."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[<img src=\"https://gitlab.tails.boum.org/tails/ux/-/raw/master/personas/personas-small.png\" id=\"picture\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Our 3 personas: Riou, Cris, and Kim\">|contribute/personas]]\n"
msgstr "[[<img src=\"https://gitlab.tails.boum.org/tails/ux/-/raw/master/personas/personas-small.png\" id=\"picture\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt =\"Les nostres 3 persones: Riou, Cris i Kim\">|contribute/personas]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This usability work was key in all the work that we did since 2015 to make "
"Tails easier to install:"
msgstr ""
"Aquest treball d'usabilitat va ser clau en tot el treball que vam fer des "
"del 2015 per facilitar la instal·lació de Tails:"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- The [[installation instructions|install]] (2016)  - The [[verification "
"extension|install/download]] (2016)  - The new [[Welcome Screen|news/"
"version_3.0#greeter]] (2017)  - The shift to [[USB images and Etcher|news/"
"version_3.12#usb-images]] (2019)"
msgstr ""
"- Les [[instruccions d'instal·lació|install]] (2016)\n"
"- L'[[extensió de verificació|install/download]] (2016)\n"
"- La nova [[Pantalla de Benvinguda|news/version_3.0#greeter]] (2017)\n"
"- El canvi a [[Imatges USB i Etcher|news/version_3.12#usb-images]] (2019)"

#. type: Title ###
#, no-wrap
msgid "Continuous integration"
msgstr "Integració contínua"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"To cope with this rapid development and the many releases, we built a "
"cutting edge *continuous integration* infrastructure:"
msgstr ""
"Per fer front a aquest desenvolupament ràpid i als nombrosos llançaments, "
"hem construït una infraestructura d'avantguarda d'*integració contínua*:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Images of Tails are [built automatically](https://nightly.tails.boum.org/) "
"every time we develop a change for an upcoming release."
msgstr ""
"Les imatges de Tails es [creen automàticament](https://nightly.tails.boum."
"org/) cada vegada que desenvolupem un canvi per a un proper llançament."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"These images are [[tested automatically|contribute/release_process/test/"
"automated_tests]] against a comprehensive list of usability and security "
"scenarios."
msgstr ""
"Aquestes imatges es [[proven automàticament|contribute/release_process/test/"
"automated_tests]] amb una llista completa d'escenaris d'usabilitat i "
"seguretat."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"All our images are [[reproducible|news/reproducible_Tails]], which allows "
"security researchers to verify that the images distributed on our website "
"have not been modified to introduce undisclosed security vulnerabilities."
msgstr ""
"Totes les nostres imatges són [[reproduïbles|news/reproducible_Tails]], el "
"que permet als investigadors de seguretat verificar que les imatges "
"distribuïdes al nostre lloc web no s'han modificat per introduir "
"vulnerabilitats de seguretat no revelades."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The following video shows the test suite in action. On the left, it displays "
"the scenario that is being tested, for example \"*symmetrically encrypting a "
"message*\". On the right, it displays Tails being manipulated automatically "
"according to the scenario."
msgstr ""
"El següent vídeo mostra la suite de proves en acció. A l'esquerra, es mostra "
"l'escenari que s'està provant, per exemple «*encriptant simètricament un "
"missatge*». A la dreta, es mostra el Tails que es manipula automàticament "
"segons l'escenari."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<video controls=\"true\" width=\"880\" height=\"352\">\n"
"  <source src=\"https://tails.net/news/celebrating_10_years/test-suite.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n"
"</video>\n"
msgstr ""
"<video controls=\"true\" width=\"880\" height=\"352\">\n"
"  <source src=\"https://tails.net/news/celebrating_10_years/test-suite.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n"
"</video>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"This infrastructure increases the quality and reliability of our releases. "
"It also makes it faster to publish emergency security releases when "
"important vulnerabilities are fixed, for example in Firefox and Tor Browser."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta infraestructura augmenta la qualitat i la fiabilitat dels nostres "
"llançaments. També fa que sigui més ràpid publicar versions de seguretat "
"d'emergència quan es solucionen vulnerabilitats importants, per exemple al "
"Firefox i al Navegador Tor."

#. type: Title ###
#, no-wrap
msgid "Project sustainability"
msgstr "Sostenibilitat del projecte"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The combination of these efforts both on visible improvements and behind the "
"scene had to go hand-in-hand with working on the sustainability of the "
"project as an organization."
msgstr ""
"La combinació d'aquests esforços tant en millores visibles com darrere de "
"l'escena havia d'anar de la mà de treballar la sostenibilitat del projecte "
"com a organització."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Since 2014:"
msgstr "Des del 2014:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The number of Tails users was multiplied by 2.4, increasing by 20% each year "
"on average, reaching 25000 daily users on average in 2019.  Our yearly "
"budget was multiplied by a similar amount, to reach 240&#8239;000€ "
"(estimated) in 2019."
msgstr ""
"El nombre d'usuaris de Tails es va multiplicar per 2'4, augmentant un 20% "
"cada any de mitjana, arribant als 25000 usuaris diaris de mitjana el 2019. "
"El nostre pressupost anual es va multiplicar per una quantitat similar, fins "
"a arribar als 240&#8239;000€ (estimat) el 2019."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We worked on foundational documents and processes to ensure a healthy "
"community and project, such as our Code of Conduct, Social Contract, and "
"[[Missions and values|contribute/mission]]."
msgstr ""
"Hem treballat en documents i processos fonamentals per garantir una "
"comunitat i un projecte saludables, com ara el nostre Codi de Conducta, "
"Contracte Social i [[Missions i valors|contribute/mission]]."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!img users-budget.svg link=\"no\" alt=\"\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!img users-budget.svg link=\"no\" alt=\"\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Sustainability cannot go without enjoying working together and having fun. "
"We had memorable gatherings where we danced to the privacy-protecting sound "
"of [Rockwell &mdash; Somebody's Watching Me](https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=7YvAYIJSSZY=), [Rap News &mdash; Whistleblower](https://www.youtube.com/"
"watch?v=7aiZjD0_mTA), [Pete Seeger &mdash; The Onion Makes Us Strong (*sic*)]"
"(https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pCnEAH5wCzo), [The Police &mdash; Every "
"Breath You Take](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OMOGaugKpzs), and [Cyndi "
"Lauper &mdash; Girls Just Want To Fix Bugs (*sic*)](https://www.youtube.com/"
"watch?v=PIb6AZdTr-A), ate delicious [[vegan mafé|mafe]] from our beloved "
"cooking team, and squashed an [[!tails_ticket 11140 desc=\"anarchist coup "
"d'état\"]]."
msgstr ""
"La sostenibilitat no pot passar sense gaudir de treballar junts i divertir-"
"nos. Vam tenir reunions memorables on vam ballar al so que protegeix la "
"privadesa de Rockwell &mdash; Somebody's Watching Me](https://www.youtube."
"com/watch?v=7YvAYIJSSZY=), [Rap News &mdash; Whistleblower](https://www."
"youtube.com/watch?v=7aiZjD0_mTA), [Pete Seeger &mdash; The Onion Makes Us "
"Strong (*sic*)](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pCnEAH5wCzo), [The Police "
"&mdash; Every Breath You Take](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OMOGaugKpzs) "
"i [Cyndi Lauper &mdash; Girls Just Want To Fix Bugs (*sic*)](https://www."
"youtube.com/watch?v=PIb6AZdTr-A), vam menjar un deliciós [[mafé vegà|mafe]] "
"del nostre estimat equip de cuina i vam aturar un [[!tails_ticket 11140 "
"desc=\"cop d'estat anarquista\"]]."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "In 2018 and 2019:"
msgstr "Durant els anys 2018 i 2019:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"66 different people contributed to our main source code, including coders, "
"writers, and translators."
msgstr ""
"66 persones diferents van contribuir al nostre codi font principal, inclosos "
"programadors, escriptors i traductors."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"22 different people were paid to work on Tails: a few of them full-time, "
"most of them part-time or as consultants."
msgstr ""
"Es van pagar 22 persones diferents per treballar a Tails: algunes d'elles a "
"temps complet, la majoria a temps parcial o com a consultors."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We attended 21 conferences in 10 different countries to stay connected with "
"the communities of the Tails ecosystem: related Free Software projects, "
"digital security trainers, and users."
msgstr ""
"Vam assistir a 21 conferències a 10 països diferents per mantenir-nos "
"connectats amb les comunitats de l'ecosistema Tails: projectes de programari "
"lliure relacionats, formadors de seguretat digital i usuaris."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "20 people, both workers and volunteers, attended our yearly gatherings."
msgstr ""
"20 persones, tant treballadors com voluntaris, van assistir a les nostres "
"trobades anuals."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Meanwhile, we counted no less than [[21 projects|doc/about/"
"acknowledgments_and_similar_projects#similar_projects]], who also tried to "
"build a live operating system for privacy and anonymity but are now "
"abandoned."
msgstr ""
"Mentrestant, vam comptar ni més ni menys que [[21 projectes|doc/about/"
"acknowledgements_and_similar_projects#similar_projects]], que també van "
"intentar construir un sistema operatiu en directe per a la privadesa i "
"l'anonimat, però ara estan abandonats."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"A big thank you to everybody who either contributed to Tails or supported us:"
msgstr ""
"Moltes gràcies a tots els que han contribuït a Tails o ens han donat suport:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "All the people mentioned in this article one way or another"
msgstr "Totes les persones esmentades en aquest article d'una manera o altra"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The people from other related Free Software projects that Tails relies upon"
msgstr ""
"La gent d'altres projectes de programari lliure relacionats en els quals "
"Tails confia"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The thousands of activists, journalists, and human-rights defenders who are "
"using Tails everyday"
msgstr ""
"Els milers d'activistes, periodistes i defensors dels drets humans que "
"utilitzen Tails cada dia"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The digital security trainers and technologists who got excited about Tails "
"in its early days and continue advocating for it today"
msgstr ""
"Els entrenadors i tecnòlegs de seguretat digital que es van entusiasmar amb "
"Tails als seus inicis i continuen defensant-lo avui"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Everybody who ever contributed to our source code, including the dozens of "
"translators"
msgstr ""
"Tots els que han contribuït alguna vegada al nostre codi font, incloses les "
"desenes de traductors"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "Our [[sponsors|sponsors]] and everybody who ever donated to Tails."
msgstr ""
"Els nostres [[patrocinadors|sponsors]] i tots els que han fet alguna donació "
"a Tails."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Thank you!"
msgstr "Moltes gràcies!"

